<h3><?=__('Boards',MCBoard::NAME_SLUG); ?></h3>
	<p><?=__('You can browse your boards from this section. You can edit any board, update its content, or delete it.',MCBoard::NAME_SLUG); ?></p>
	<p><?=__('You can also create new boards by clicking on the <em>Create a New Board</em> button. Be sure to <em>update</em> its content once it\'s created: It will reduce the load time of your pages on the front-end.',MCBoard::NAME_SLUG); ?></p>
	<p><?=__('After that, they will be automatically updated every hour or so.',MCBoard::NAME_SLUG); ?></p>
